commit.message:
Use new js_of_ocaml META standard to link JavaScript stubs.

Closes #28.

Non strict Ptime.of_rfc3339: lenient timezone offset parsing.

Closes #31.

Add ?tz_offset_s optional argument to Ptime.{to,of}_date.

Closes #32.
Doc: work around odoc xref failures.
Build system: allow to define OS via PTIME_OS (like we do in mtime).
Drop `ptime.clock.jsoo`, dune users won't see the deprecation anyways.

Add a comment on odd looking check in floating point conversions.

And correct a potential overflow if it may actually happen
in Ptime.Span.of_float_s.

Closes #26.
Bow to OCaml's new default warnings.

Tweak formatting of last commit and add copyright headers.

Also make `dmin` match the value of `Ptime.min`.
